As for the number of deaths, the numbers in the Facebook post are correct with respect to one outbreak.
Total estimated deaths, according to the CDC: 1 million, including 100,000 in the United States.
Other sources, including GlobalSecurity.org, refer to 1 million deaths or in the range of 750,000 to 1 million deaths (Medscape medical website, Nieman Foundation for Journalism).